import teamMemberTags from './teamMemberTags'; 

const teamMembers = [
    {
        name: 'Anri', 
        description: 'Role',
        imageUrl: process.env.PUBLIC_URL + 'assets/Anri.png',
        tags: teamMemberTags[0], 
        bio: ` 
                Similarly, people have always been communicating 
                and organizing in large scales and across boundaries. 
                Currently, we are on the precipice of cultural, environmental, 
                and sociopolitical upheaval. This means that we need better 
                tools for this process. Our team is building Campfire to be a 
                space that facilitates communication and knowledge production.
            `,
        
    }, 

    {
        name: 'Jenny', 
        description: 'Role',
        imageUrl: process.env.PUBLIC_URL + 'assets/Jenny.png',
        tags: teamMemberTags[1], 
        bio: ` 
                this is my bio

    }, 

    {

        description: 'Role',
        imageUrl: process.env.PUBLIC_URL + 'assets/Min.png',
        tags: teamMemberTags[2], 
        bio: ` 
                this is my bio 
            `,
    }, 

    {
        name: 'Sylvia', 
        description: 'Role',
        imageUrl: process.env.PUBLIC_URL + 'assets/Sylvia.png',
        tags: teamMemberTags[3], 
        bio: ` 
                this is my bio 
            `,
    }, 

    {
        name: 'Vanessa', 
        description: 'Role',
        imageUrl: process.env.PUBLIC_URL + 'assets/Vanessa.png',
        tags: teamMemberTags[4], 
        bio: ` 
                this is my bio 
            `,
    }, 

]; 

export default teamMembers;
